import React, { useState } from "react"; import { Container, Typography, Paper, Box, Button, Avatar, Grid, Table, TableBody, TableCell, TableContainer, TableHead, TableRow, } from "@mui/material"; import { orange } from "@mui/material/colors"; const UserProfile = () => { const [user] = useState({ name: "Nikhil", email: "nikhil@example.com", dob: "1900-01-01", activities: [ { type: "Logged in", time: "2025-03-26 20:05:50", ip: "103.81.93.51" }, { type: "Logged in", time: "2025-03-20 14:00:12", ip: "103.161.99.176" }, { type: "Logged out", time: "2025-03-20 14:00:02", ip: "103.161.99.176" }, { type: "Security Answer updated", time: "2025-03-20 13:51:48", ip: "103.161.99.176" }, { type: "Logged in", time: "2025-03-20 13:50:51", ip: "103.161.99.176" }, { type: "Account Created", time: "2025-03-20 13:50:29", ip: "103.161.99.176" }, ], }); return ( U {user.name} Learner Personal Details Name: {user.name} Email: {user.email} DOB: {user.dob} Recent Activities # Type Time IP {user.activities.map((activity, index) => ( {index + 1} {activity.type} {activity.time} {activity.ip} ))}
); }; export default UserProfile;
